data.description: *Ernest Homes popular St. Helena floor plan. 4/2.5, 1,921 sq. ft. of air conditioned space. *Under construction. *Estimated completion middle of August 2021. *Pic's are from a previously built St. Helena. Located on a quiet cul de sac with private wooded back yard. Come experience our quality of construction and open floor plan. *All bedrooms up. Beautiful granite kitchen counter tops with 42" upper cabinets and tile back splash. Stainless kitchen appliances. Upgraded LVT flooring in living areas. Marble counter tops in 2nd bath and master. Master bath equipped with dual vanity and separate shower and garden tub. Larger 5.25" base boards through out the home. Spacious master bedroom with tray ceiling. *Spray foam insulation *Pic's are of a previously built St. Helena. *Price is subject to change based on current market conditions.
